title: Gamma Ray - The Best Of Gamma Ray 320k  2015 ak6103
description:
The Best (Of) is a compilation album of German power metal band Gamma Ray, released on 30th January 2015.

The Best (Of) has been released as 2-disc Standard Edition, 4-vinyl-Gatefold and a high-quality 2-disc Limited Edition in an elaborate and exclusive leather-style package. All tracks were remastered in 2014 by Eike Freese.
